sect1.title: External Interfaces
sect1.para:
The external interfaces of UDSServices are described by the in the SWA at the following location in Enterprise Architect: VW_ICAS1.Chorus.All_Cores.SoftwareDecomposition.ComplexDeviceDrivers.UDS_Service_Chorus.SW Architecture.UDSServiceHandler
A part of the external interfaces used by UDSServices is provided by the component "RTE Light QM" and includes generated interfaces which are based on the following SST files: SST_UDSServiceHandler.xlsx: mc_sw see also Component Diagram "SW Architecture" at the following location in Enterprise Architect: VW_ICAS1.Chorus.All_Cores.SoftwareDecomposition.ComplexDeviceDrivers.UDS_Service_Chorus.SW Architecture.UDSServiceHandler.Integration context

sect1.title: External Dependencies
sect1.para: The external dependencies of UDSServices are described by the Component Diagram "UDSServices dependencies" in the SWA at the following location in Enterprise Architect: VW_ICAS1.Chorus.All_Cores.SoftwareDecomposition.ComplexDeviceDrivers.UDS_Service_Chorus.SW Architecture.UDSServiceHandler.Integration context
